{"tid":172262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西腐肉醜聞風波　中國已取消禁令","createTime":"2017-03-25T19:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T04:51:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"57bfa617d79b317c5204d9ff05976868285b5a3c","tid":172262,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T19:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170325/photo/bknint-20170325061938156-0325_17011_001_01p.jpg?20170325230341\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170325%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170325061938156-0325_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170325230341&h=36346eb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴西政府下令3公司被下令回收肉類產品。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n巴西消費者保護組織Senacom周五下令3間涉及腐肉醜聞的肉類包裝公司，回收售出的肉類產品。不過，巴西農業部長及後發出聲明，指中國已經取消入口禁令。<br />\n<br />\n組織的聲明說，Souza Ramos、Transmeat和Peccin公司在南部巴拉那州營運的3個工場，必須在5日內回收產品。該組織說，農業部擔心Peccin公司的肉類可能有健康風險，以及Souza Ramos 和Transmeat產品缺乏監管和難以追查的措施。Senacom回應當局的關注，發出回收命令。巴西有21間公司涉及出售腐肉而遭調調查，上述3間公司是其中調查對象。<br />\n<br />\n巴西龐大的肉食業因醜聞而受到重大打擊，包括中國的主要市場紛紛停止進口所有巴西肉類，歐盟則禁止輸入涉案公司的肉類產品。香港周五宣布回收21間巴西凍肉公司已進口香港的肉類，早前發出對巴西所有肉類的進口禁令繼續維持。<br />\n<br />\n巴西農業部長於當地時間周六發出聲明，指中國政府已取消對巴西肉類的入口禁令，重新開發入口。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170325/bknint-20170325061938156-0325_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170325%2Fbknint-20170325061938156-0325_17011_001.html&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=a68b5deb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170325/bknint-20170325061938156-0325_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"37673a00e399685927c99b1fe971f52d5d10ee14","tid":172262,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T19:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6ddbaad527ef413fc6950e1b22aab5927f7e22","tid":172262,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T20:00:12.000Z","msg":"啲肉好平？咁大舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8652ebf5ad63501d189cd5dfdf93503626094bbc","tid":172262,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T20:03:06.000Z","msg":"咁香港啲買家唔使蝕咁多<br />\n可以轉手買上中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住當中國冷藏肉運返來香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7c40f4ed269c23bd901edda85d9db4b9f548b5","tid":172262,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T20:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0c6b7b8201936d0d951eccf5c35efd0598afe5","tid":172262,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T21:40:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁香港啲買家唔使蝕咁多<br />\n可以轉手買上中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住當中國冷藏肉運返來香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6633f20cf43f1257ad335382fc052b7377fb9e2","tid":172262,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T00:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc11578e2f58a9968751dcdaff85ee390c7290b","tid":172262,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T00:53:35.000Z","msg":"金豬四國友好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef2a3eb94ff4200ef638dc78d203fa358c6536d","tid":172262,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T01:40:38.000Z","msg":"德政 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那人起碼有真肉食先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81270fc2288e7a12cce4b1700d5663d84dbd711c","tid":172262,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0